text: This church have 2 services, korean service and bahasa Malaysia service especially for local people, sabah, sarawak and indonesia. Students, families are welcome..

This is Johor Bahru Full Gospel Korean Church.
The senior pastor has been doing indigenous missionary work and Korean church ministry in Kuala Lumpur and the jungles of Malaysia for over 20 years.
A church full of praise, a church full of words,
A church alive with prayer, full of fellowship among believers
This is Johor Bahru Full Gospel Church.

There are some people who have prejudices against the Full Gospel Church~^^ It is not that kind of atmosphere, so please feel free to come. It is a wonderful church centered on the Word and missions. It is a missionary church with local (Bahasa) churches as well.
I was touched by the blessings of the pastor's sermon and the welcome of the congregation^^
